1
00:01:53,479 --> 00:01:54,920
I, Fei Zheng, swear

2
00:01:55,150 --> 00:01:56,590
that even though I am in Jinglan,

3
00:01:56,590 --> 00:01:59,070
I will obey Changmo’s orders
at all times,

4
00:01:59,280 --> 00:02:00,400
even at the cost of my life.

5
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:01,350
If I break this vow,

6
00:02:01,350 --> 00:02:03,150
may I die without a burial place.

7
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:10,310
This token

8
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:12,710
represents the King of Mo himself.

9
00:02:12,710 --> 00:02:13,770
You recognized me.

10
00:02:13,870 --> 00:02:16,000
I believe when we first met,

11
00:02:17,190 --> 00:02:18,520
you recognized me, too.

12
00:02:19,430 --> 00:02:20,430
As Changmo’s

13
00:02:20,430 --> 00:02:22,230
deepest-placed spy in Jinglan,

14
00:02:23,150 --> 00:02:25,480
how could you forget an old acquaintance?

15
00:02:26,150 --> 00:02:27,079
What do you want?

16
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:29,870
You have been undercover
in Jinglan for years.

17
00:02:29,870 --> 00:02:30,470
And now,

18
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:32,590
you are the Minister of Revenue.

19
00:02:32,590 --> 00:02:33,910
The Hall Master believes

20
00:02:33,910 --> 00:02:35,370
it’s time to activate you.

21
00:02:38,590 --> 00:02:41,050
What makes you think
I’ll let him control me?

22
00:02:41,750 --> 00:02:43,010
You swore a blood oath.

23
00:02:43,310 --> 00:02:44,310
Blood oath?

24
00:02:44,750 --> 00:02:46,680
You know what happens to traitors.

25
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:49,310
Do you want me to fail the mission

26
00:02:49,750 --> 00:02:50,960
and end up like them?

27
00:03:01,590 --> 00:03:02,240
Tell me.

28
00:03:03,470 --> 00:03:05,530
What mission did you bring this time?

29
00:03:05,630 --> 00:03:07,160
First, escort the princess

30
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:08,240
safely to Jinglan

31
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:10,370
for the marriage alliance.

32
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:11,810
The second is

33
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:15,040
to awaken you.

34
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:18,750
Years of planning have now
been set in motion.

35
00:03:18,750 --> 00:03:20,810
There’s no turning back for any of us.

36
00:03:33,470 --> 00:03:34,150
Stop!

37
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:35,120
Stop!

38
00:03:35,190 --> 00:03:35,850
Don't move!

39
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:36,470
Stop!

40
00:03:36,710 --> 00:03:38,520
Stop. Stop right there!

41
00:03:38,750 --> 00:03:39,750
Everybody, stop!

42
00:03:42,630 --> 00:03:43,360
Stop!

43
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:44,680
Don't move!

44
00:03:45,190 --> 00:03:46,750
Every mountain has its master,

45
00:03:46,750 --> 00:03:47,630
What happened?

46
00:03:47,630 --> 00:03:48,680
and every road has its lord.

47
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:49,360
Don't worry.

48
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:50,030
Today,

49
00:03:50,030 --> 00:03:50,710
They are just a few bandits.

50
00:03:50,710 --> 00:03:52,190
if you want to pass,

51
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:54,710
leave your money behind.

52
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:01,140
Do you even know who we are?

53
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:03,370
You dare to rob government officials?

54
00:04:04,590 --> 00:04:06,150
They are government officials.

55
00:04:06,150 --> 00:04:06,750
So what?

56
00:04:07,030 --> 00:04:08,560
So what if they are government officials?

57
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:09,590
We outnumber them.

58
00:04:09,590 --> 00:04:10,680
Yes, we are not afraid of you.

59
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:11,630
We have more people!

60
00:04:11,630 --> 00:04:13,080
We are almost at the capital.

61
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:14,400
How could something like this happen?

62
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:15,750
West of the capital
isn’t like the main pass.

63
00:04:15,750 --> 00:04:17,310
These are narrow backroads.

64
00:04:17,310 --> 00:04:19,160
In these remote
and impoverished backwaters,

65
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:21,600
it is inevitable that ruffians
will commit evil deeds.

66
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:22,130
Hurry up.

67
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:24,700
Chengfeng.

68
00:04:24,830 --> 00:04:25,920
Yes, General.

69
00:04:33,870 --> 00:04:34,430
Boss.

70
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:35,210
Get them!

71
00:04:35,270 --> 00:04:35,750
Get them!

72
00:04:35,750 --> 00:04:36,870
G-Get them!

73
00:04:42,870 --> 00:04:43,310
Run!

74
00:04:43,870 --> 00:04:44,360
Run!

75
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:47,850
Mercy, my lords!

76
00:04:48,159 --> 00:04:48,720
Stop hitting us.

77
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:49,360
Stop hitting us.

78
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:51,159
Highway robbery is a capital offense.

79
00:04:51,159 --> 00:04:52,560
Do you still want to live?

80
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:53,950
We had no choice.

81
00:04:54,310 --> 00:04:56,480
Last month, an official came,

82
00:04:56,560 --> 00:04:58,720
saying he was a servant
of Lord Wang from the court.

83
00:04:58,720 --> 00:05:00,310
He set their sights on our village land.

84
00:05:00,310 --> 00:05:02,070
He claimed our village
had excellent feng shui

85
00:05:02,070 --> 00:05:03,310
and wanted to build a tomb

86
00:05:03,310 --> 00:05:05,160
for Lord Wang’s
recently deceased concubine.

87
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:05,680
So,

88
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:07,680
they drove all of us out.

89
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:08,830
Yes, yes, yes.

90
00:05:10,190 --> 00:05:10,790
Lord Wang?

91
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:11,950
Wang Ruhai?

92
00:05:12,040 --> 00:05:14,310
One of the 3 ministers appointed
by the late emperor—

93
00:05:14,310 --> 00:05:15,440
If I'm not mistaken,

94
00:05:15,630 --> 00:05:16,290
that's him.

95
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:18,600
What a scoundrel.

96
00:05:19,270 --> 00:05:21,330
Even his servant dares
to seize land.

97
00:05:21,430 --> 00:05:23,040
We only rob the rich to help the poor.

98
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:24,040
We only rob the rich.

99
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:25,310
We let the poor go.

100
00:05:25,510 --> 00:05:26,560
-Yes.
-My lords.

101
00:05:26,560 --> 00:05:28,020
Please spare us this time.

102
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:30,080
Why should I believe you?

103
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:32,750
Stop hiding.

104
00:05:32,750 --> 00:05:33,360
Come out.

105
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:34,000
Come ou!.

106
00:05:34,070 --> 00:05:35,240
E-Everyone, come out.

107
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:36,870
E-Everyone, come out.

108
00:05:43,310 --> 00:05:44,170
Look, my lords,

109
00:05:44,310 --> 00:05:45,640
what we said is all true.

110
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:48,780
Chengfeng.

111
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:49,650
Yes, sir.

112
00:05:50,310 --> 00:05:51,510
Give them some money.

113
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:52,770
Yes, sir.

114
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:57,510
Take this money

115
00:05:58,270 --> 00:06:00,000
and find a place to settle down.

116
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:02,560
Someone will see justice done for you.

117
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:03,510
Thank you, my lords.

118
00:06:03,510 --> 00:06:04,360
Thank you, my lords.

119
00:06:04,360 --> 00:06:05,870
Thank you, my lords.

120
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:07,520
-Let's go.
-Don't worry.

121
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:09,240
When we return to the capital,

122
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:12,170
I will report this matter truthfully
to His Majesty.

123
00:06:13,270 --> 00:06:14,040
Let me say it.

124
00:06:14,510 --> 00:06:15,110
After all,

125
00:06:15,310 --> 00:06:17,120
you have to work with them in the court,

126
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:18,920
while I am far away at the border.

127
00:06:20,070 --> 00:06:20,430
Hyah!

128
00:06:23,390 --> 00:06:23,830
Hyah!

129
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:29,330
Look.

130
00:06:29,750 --> 00:06:30,600
So?

131
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:33,000
Do I carry myself like the Son of Heaven?

132
00:06:33,159 --> 00:06:34,480
Your Majesty, you were born

133
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:36,510
with the bearing of the Son of Heaven.

134
00:06:36,510 --> 00:06:37,310
Of course.

135
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:43,360
Greetings, Your Majesty.

136
00:06:44,159 --> 00:06:44,890
You are here.

137
00:06:45,159 --> 00:06:46,159
Come, take a look.

138
00:06:46,270 --> 00:06:47,720
If I wear this

139
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:50,250
to welcome General Xiao, how does it look?

140
00:06:50,750 --> 00:06:51,560
Your Majesty.

141
00:06:52,159 --> 00:06:54,000
Why is there no morning court today?

142
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:55,680
Where have

143
00:06:56,159 --> 00:06:57,190
all the ministers gone?

144
00:06:57,190 --> 00:06:57,750
Today,

145
00:06:57,920 --> 00:06:59,310
Xiao Chi and Fei Zheng

146
00:06:59,310 --> 00:07:00,920
are escorting the princess back.

147
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:01,720
I sent them

148
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:03,190
to the city gates to welcome them.

149
00:07:03,190 --> 00:07:04,360
Once they are welcomed back,

150
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:06,160
-we will...
-Since ancient times,

151
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:08,000
the state has always come first.

152
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:08,920
Your Majesty,

153
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:11,800
how could you dismiss the court

154
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:14,680
to welcome a border general?

155
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:16,240
Yes, Your Majesty.

156
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:18,190
Xiao Chi is nothing but a brute soldier.

157
00:07:18,190 --> 00:07:19,510
What right does he have

158
00:07:19,510 --> 00:07:21,430
to have so many court ministers

159
00:07:21,430 --> 00:07:23,120
welcome him together?

160
00:07:23,390 --> 00:07:25,680
This is against proper court etiquette.

161
00:07:26,070 --> 00:07:27,870
Yes, you are the lord,

162
00:07:28,070 --> 00:07:29,310
and he is the subject.

163
00:07:29,630 --> 00:07:32,000
Doing this will only fuel

164
00:07:32,159 --> 00:07:34,430
his arrogance.

165
00:07:35,070 --> 00:07:36,720
Yes, Your Majesty.

166
00:07:37,190 --> 00:07:37,990
Your Majesty.

167
00:07:38,190 --> 00:07:40,560
Do you know where this is?

168
00:07:42,270 --> 00:07:43,310
This is

169
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:46,310
the Hall of Diligent Governance.

170
00:07:46,310 --> 00:07:48,000
For the sake of a mere warrior,

171
00:07:48,190 --> 00:07:50,190
you would even skip court.

172
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:55,200
Well, the Hall of Diligent Governance
will have to change its name afterwards.

173
00:07:55,750 --> 00:07:57,750
Seeing Your Majesty like this,

174
00:07:58,159 --> 00:07:59,270
we have truly

175
00:07:59,510 --> 00:08:02,560
failed the late emperor’s trust.

176
00:08:02,870 --> 00:08:04,430
Even after we die,

177
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:07,800
we will be too ashamed
to face the late emperor.

178
00:08:07,870 --> 00:08:09,800
We have failed the late emperor.

179
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:11,800
It won’t come to that, surely.

180
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:13,920
Next time, before making such decisions,

181
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:16,600
I will consult with you first.

182
00:08:16,950 --> 00:08:18,270
Next time?

183
00:08:18,870 --> 00:08:20,870
What about this time?

184
00:08:21,190 --> 00:08:23,750
Your Majesty, you are the Son of Heaven,

185
00:08:23,750 --> 00:08:25,560
even you should be punished

186
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:27,240
for wrongdoing.

187
00:08:27,510 --> 00:08:29,630
Y-Yes, exactly.

188
00:08:31,270 --> 00:08:32,270
What punishment?

189
00:08:33,909 --> 00:08:34,669
Well...

190
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:36,150
How about this?

191
00:08:36,150 --> 00:08:37,390
Your Majesty shall be punished

192
00:08:37,390 --> 00:08:40,789
to copy the late Emperor's instructions
10 times.

193
00:08:41,030 --> 00:08:42,240
10 times?

194
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:42,750
Yes.

195
00:08:42,870 --> 00:08:43,320
Yes.

196
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:45,270
Only after completing them

197
00:08:45,270 --> 00:08:47,840
may you see Xiao Chi and Fei Zheng.

198
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:48,960
Okay.

199
00:08:49,790 --> 00:08:50,600
I understand.

200
00:08:52,910 --> 00:08:55,360
We will take our leave.

201
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:57,320
I... I shall take my leave.

202
00:08:57,320 --> 00:08:58,320
Take my leave.

203
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:08,270
What are you looking at me for?

204
00:09:08,270 --> 00:09:10,470
Prepare the writing materials at once.

205
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:11,660
Yes, Your Majesty.

206
00:09:25,320 --> 00:09:28,790
Welcome back to the capital, Lord Fei.

207
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:32,510
Welcome back to the capital, General Xiao.

208
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:35,320
Wow.

209
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:37,320
-Is this...
-Your Highness.

210
00:09:49,120 --> 00:09:50,600
His Majesty decrees:

211
00:09:50,790 --> 00:09:54,080
Princess Peace of Changmo shall stay
at the post house temporarily.

212
00:09:54,080 --> 00:09:57,540
Lord Fei and General Xiao are
to enter the palace immediately.

213
00:09:58,870 --> 00:10:00,200
We obey His Majesty's command.

214
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:02,320
It’s quite different from Changmo.

215
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:06,240
It is.

216
00:10:08,750 --> 00:10:10,350
What are they talking about?

217
00:10:10,750 --> 00:10:11,610
Your Highness.

218
00:10:11,790 --> 00:10:13,080
Mind your conduct.

219
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:16,260
Chengfeng,

220
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:19,200
have Physician Han stay
at the post house with the princess.

221
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:19,910
Keep an eye on them.

222
00:10:19,910 --> 00:10:20,630
I will return shortly.

223
00:10:20,630 --> 00:10:21,430
Yes, General.

224
00:10:22,120 --> 00:10:22,650
Let's go.

225
00:10:30,750 --> 00:10:35,120
Long live the Emperor!

226
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:35,910
Rise.

227
00:10:36,270 --> 00:10:37,200
Rise, all of you.

228
00:10:38,870 --> 00:10:39,510
Xiao Chi.

229
00:10:40,150 --> 00:10:40,750
Fei Zheng.

230
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:43,030
You two have traveled a long way.

231
00:10:43,030 --> 00:10:44,240
You must be weary from the journey.

232
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:45,500
I missed Your Majesty,

233
00:10:45,750 --> 00:10:47,750
so I hastened back without delay.

234
00:10:48,120 --> 00:10:49,480
It's good that you're back.

235
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:50,360
General Xiao,

236
00:10:50,750 --> 00:10:52,630
you've guarded the border for years

237
00:10:52,630 --> 00:10:54,320
and made great contributions.

238
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:54,960
Next,

239
00:10:55,240 --> 00:10:58,300
I intend to have you transfer
to the capital's defense.

240
00:10:58,600 --> 00:11:00,730
Don't go back to Tianlang Pass for now.

241
00:11:01,200 --> 00:11:02,000
Your Majesty.

242
00:11:02,600 --> 00:11:05,670
General Xiao has guarded Tianlang Pass
for years.

243
00:11:05,790 --> 00:11:09,390
Replacing a general
at such a time is a grave taboo.

244
00:11:09,790 --> 00:11:10,550
Yes.

245
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:12,320
Lord Zhang,

246
00:11:12,750 --> 00:11:13,950
you made a fair point.

247
00:11:14,550 --> 00:11:15,350
Your Majesty.

248
00:11:15,790 --> 00:11:17,120
the Princess of Changmo

249
00:11:17,510 --> 00:11:19,030
has safely arrived in the capital.

250
00:11:19,030 --> 00:11:20,600
We await Your Majesty’s instruction

251
00:11:20,600 --> 00:11:22,120
for the marriage alliance.

252
00:11:22,120 --> 00:11:23,870
It's good that you brought her back.

253
00:11:23,870 --> 00:11:26,670
The marriage alliance needs
to be arranged carefully.

254
00:11:26,670 --> 00:11:28,000
This marriage alliance

255
00:11:28,030 --> 00:11:31,270
must be conducted according
to Jinglan rites.

256
00:11:31,840 --> 00:11:33,570
Lord Wang is absolutely right.

257
00:11:33,840 --> 00:11:36,150
The etiquette of Jinglan
is extremely complex.

258
00:11:36,150 --> 00:11:38,390
As the acting Minister of Rites,

259
00:11:38,510 --> 00:11:40,670
it indeed requires careful consideration.

260
00:11:40,670 --> 00:11:41,510
Yes.

261
00:11:42,790 --> 00:11:45,910
General Xiao, you've faced Changmo
for years.

262
00:11:46,270 --> 00:11:47,630
Returning this time,

263
00:11:47,670 --> 00:11:49,790
do you have any good news for us?

264
00:11:49,870 --> 00:11:51,270
Any news from the border?

265
00:11:51,550 --> 00:11:53,720
Changmo has invaded repeatedly
but never broken through.

266
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:54,980
Thanks to His Majesty,

267
00:11:55,030 --> 00:11:56,030
the people live in peace,

268
00:11:56,030 --> 00:11:57,390
and we have bountiful harvests every year.

269
00:11:57,390 --> 00:11:58,050
Would these

270
00:11:58,390 --> 00:12:00,600
count as good news, Lord Wang?

271
00:12:00,960 --> 00:12:02,000
Yes, yes, yes.

272
00:12:02,440 --> 00:12:03,080
Oh, right.

273
00:12:03,510 --> 00:12:05,310
I have 2 more pieces of good news.

274
00:12:05,960 --> 00:12:07,890
I brought the Border Special Envoy

275
00:12:08,120 --> 00:12:09,390
Zhao Gao back with me.

276
00:12:09,480 --> 00:12:10,240
Lord Wang,

277
00:12:10,480 --> 00:12:12,600
you can catch up with him.

278
00:12:13,550 --> 00:12:16,030
His Majesty didn't summon him back.

279
00:12:16,630 --> 00:12:18,630
How could you act on your own

280
00:12:18,630 --> 00:12:20,320
and bring him back to the capital?

281
00:12:20,320 --> 00:12:21,200
Zhao Gao,

282
00:12:21,510 --> 00:12:23,600
went to the border as a Special Envoy

283
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:25,630
but never visited the military camp.

284
00:12:25,630 --> 00:12:27,240
He drank and made merry every day,

285
00:12:27,240 --> 00:12:30,240
and even tried to force
a Changmo woman into marriage.

286
00:12:31,240 --> 00:12:34,720
He was merely negligent on occasion.

287
00:12:34,910 --> 00:12:35,440
Does that

288
00:12:35,670 --> 00:12:37,550
violate your military law?

289
00:12:37,840 --> 00:12:39,480
In our Jinglan military law,

290
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:42,840
which clause forbids drinking at home

291
00:12:42,870 --> 00:12:46,120
or marrying a woman from an enemy state?

292
00:12:46,910 --> 00:12:47,510
Lord Wang,

293
00:12:47,910 --> 00:12:49,870
you are indeed very protective
of your nephew.

294
00:12:49,870 --> 00:12:50,390
Yes.

295
00:12:51,030 --> 00:12:52,360
I haven't finished yet.

296
00:12:53,240 --> 00:12:54,000
Zhao Gao

297
00:12:54,200 --> 00:12:56,240
embezzled 800,000 taels of military funds.

298
00:12:56,240 --> 00:12:58,600
Lord Wang, you must
have had a hand in this.

299
00:13:03,320 --> 00:13:04,080
Xiao Chi,

300
00:13:04,600 --> 00:13:06,080
what nonsense are you talking about?

301
00:13:06,080 --> 00:13:08,150
I know nothing of this matter.

302
00:13:08,750 --> 00:13:09,870
Do you really not know?

303
00:13:09,870 --> 00:13:10,150
I...

304
00:13:11,320 --> 00:13:11,600
I...

305
00:13:12,120 --> 00:13:12,840
don't know!

306
00:13:13,630 --> 00:13:14,390
Fine.

307
00:13:14,840 --> 00:13:16,970
I'll assume you don't know, Lord Wang.

308
00:13:18,240 --> 00:13:21,000
Yet you permitted your servants
to forcibly seize land in Qingshan Village

309
00:13:21,000 --> 00:13:22,670
to build a tomb for your concubine.

310
00:13:22,670 --> 00:13:24,470
You must know about that, right?

311
00:13:24,600 --> 00:13:25,270
The villagers were driven
from their homes

312
00:13:25,270 --> 00:13:26,390
and left destitute.

313
00:13:26,390 --> 00:13:28,030
I saw this with my own eyes.

314
00:13:28,960 --> 00:13:31,630
You sent your nephew
to the border as a Special Envoy.

315
00:13:31,630 --> 00:13:32,630
If he abided by the law

316
00:13:32,630 --> 00:13:34,120
and rendered distinguished service,

317
00:13:34,120 --> 00:13:35,720
it would have counted
as a great merit to your name.

318
00:13:35,720 --> 00:13:38,510
But he embezzled 800,000 taels
of military funds.

319
00:13:38,510 --> 00:13:40,270
And you permitted your servants
to seize land,

320
00:13:40,270 --> 00:13:42,000
leaving the people destitute.

321
00:13:42,600 --> 00:13:43,200
You are a key minister appointed

322
00:13:43,200 --> 00:13:45,530
by the late Emperor to assist His Majesty.

323
00:13:45,670 --> 00:13:47,030
For committing such acts,

324
00:13:47,030 --> 00:13:48,830
what punishment do you deserve?

325
00:13:49,720 --> 00:13:50,720
Do calm yourself.

326
00:13:51,600 --> 00:13:52,360
Xiao Chi,

327
00:13:52,550 --> 00:13:53,720
as soon as you return,

328
00:13:53,720 --> 00:13:56,720
you openly accuse a senior minister
of the court.

329
00:13:57,150 --> 00:13:59,150
Where does that leave His Majesty?

330
00:13:59,630 --> 00:14:00,910
Where do you put

331
00:14:00,910 --> 00:14:04,200
the 3 ministers entrusted
by the late Emperor

332
00:14:04,200 --> 00:14:05,150
to His Majesty?

333
00:14:05,150 --> 00:14:06,680
-Exactly.
-And Lord Zhang,

334
00:14:07,390 --> 00:14:09,790
what is your attitude towards His Majesty?

335
00:14:10,120 --> 00:14:12,320
Where do you leave His Majesty?

336
00:14:12,670 --> 00:14:14,840
Could it be that Lord Wang’s dealings

337
00:14:15,360 --> 00:14:16,360
also involve you, Lord Zhang?

338
00:14:16,360 --> 00:14:16,820
This...

339
00:14:17,080 --> 00:14:18,240
What are you talking about?

340
00:14:18,240 --> 00:14:19,670
How would I know?

341
00:14:19,910 --> 00:14:20,670
In that case,

342
00:14:21,270 --> 00:14:22,440
I respectfully request Your Majesty

343
00:14:22,440 --> 00:14:24,600
to strip Wang Ruhai
of his rank and titles.

344
00:14:24,600 --> 00:14:25,870
After the truth is found out,

345
00:14:25,870 --> 00:14:28,360
Your Majesty can decide
how to deal with him.

346
00:14:28,790 --> 00:14:29,270
You—

347
00:14:31,790 --> 00:14:32,670
Your Majesty.

348
00:14:33,240 --> 00:14:34,270
I am wronged!

349
00:14:34,550 --> 00:14:36,550
Xiao Chi is slandering me.

350
00:14:36,670 --> 00:14:38,440
I don't know anything about these things.

351
00:14:38,440 --> 00:14:40,480
I don't know them at all!

352
00:14:42,080 --> 00:14:42,880
Your Majesty,

353
00:14:43,030 --> 00:14:44,510
Qingshan Village is small,

354
00:14:44,510 --> 00:14:47,710
but who knows how many Qingshan Villages
are behind this.

355
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:49,910
The matter of military funds
is of great importance.

356
00:14:49,910 --> 00:14:52,200
I think it must be investigated.

357
00:14:53,150 --> 00:14:53,750
Lord Wang,

358
00:14:54,670 --> 00:14:57,150
whether General Xiao
is making false accusations,

359
00:14:57,150 --> 00:15:00,510
once Zhao Gao and the villagers
of Qingshan are interrogated,

360
00:15:00,510 --> 00:15:02,840
His Majesty will give you a fair judgment.

361
00:15:03,150 --> 00:15:04,350
-I...
-Your Majesty.

362
00:15:04,960 --> 00:15:07,000
We are all ministers

363
00:15:07,000 --> 00:15:09,150
entrusted to you by the late emperor.

364
00:15:09,150 --> 00:15:11,630
You must not act on one-sided testimony

365
00:15:11,750 --> 00:15:13,720
and punish anyone of us.

366
00:15:13,720 --> 00:15:14,200
Yeah.

367
00:15:14,200 --> 00:15:15,630
Yes, Your Majesty.

368
00:15:18,870 --> 00:15:19,750
I think

369
00:15:20,320 --> 00:15:22,320
what you all said makes sense.

370
00:15:23,080 --> 00:15:25,270
There is no need to rush to judgment.

371
00:15:25,750 --> 00:15:26,410
Wang Ruhai,

372
00:15:27,240 --> 00:15:28,700
you go home and rest first.

373
00:15:29,080 --> 00:15:31,080
Once the truth is established,

374
00:15:31,200 --> 00:15:32,390
I will make a decision.

375
00:15:32,390 --> 00:15:32,670
I...

376
00:15:33,510 --> 00:15:33,970
This...

377
00:15:34,030 --> 00:15:34,910
He... He...

378
00:15:35,240 --> 00:15:35,750
Your Majesty.

379
00:15:35,750 --> 00:15:36,410
Lord Zhang.

380
00:15:37,150 --> 00:15:39,080
Your Majesty, as the Son of Heaven,

381
00:15:39,510 --> 00:15:41,550
he is also the late emperor’s
sole legitimate successor.

382
00:15:41,550 --> 00:15:44,150
Lord Zhang, are you going
to disobey his order?

383
00:15:44,240 --> 00:15:44,600
I...

384
00:15:47,720 --> 00:15:48,240
Okay.

385
00:15:48,720 --> 00:15:50,120
Then it's settled.

386
00:15:50,390 --> 00:15:50,840
I...

387
00:15:51,200 --> 00:15:52,390
What do you think,

388
00:15:52,750 --> 00:15:53,550
my ministers?

389
00:15:54,320 --> 00:15:56,120
We shall leave it at that for now.

390
00:15:59,840 --> 00:16:01,370
If there are no objections,

391
00:16:01,630 --> 00:16:02,270
the court

392
00:16:03,510 --> 00:16:04,480
is adjourned.

393
00:16:05,120 --> 00:16:07,630
We'll take our leave.

394
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:10,330
All of you may withdraw.

395
00:16:10,630 --> 00:16:11,510
-Yes.
-Yes.

396
00:16:12,120 --> 00:16:13,270
You, too, get out.

397
00:16:13,270 --> 00:16:13,910
Yes.

398
00:16:15,240 --> 00:16:16,670
Why are you still standing there?

399
00:16:16,670 --> 00:16:17,790
If I leave,

400
00:16:17,790 --> 00:16:19,270
who will attend to Your Majesty?

401
00:16:19,270 --> 00:16:21,200
Just get out when I tell you to.

402
00:16:21,200 --> 00:16:22,790
Why all this talk?

403
00:16:22,790 --> 00:16:23,480
Yes.

404
00:16:24,630 --> 00:16:25,390
Without my orders,

405
00:16:25,390 --> 00:16:26,440
no one is allowed in.

406
00:16:26,440 --> 00:16:27,080
Yes.

407
00:16:29,870 --> 00:16:30,480
All right.

408
00:16:31,480 --> 00:16:32,210
Let's begin.

409
00:16:32,320 --> 00:16:34,440
Just as we did back at the manor.

410
00:16:34,840 --> 00:16:36,840
Like in the manor?

411
00:16:37,480 --> 00:16:39,150
Would this not be against the rules?

412
00:16:39,150 --> 00:16:40,720
Forget the rules.

413
00:16:40,720 --> 00:16:42,380
I have already sent them away.

414
00:16:42,630 --> 00:16:43,750
But... Your Majesty...

415
00:16:43,750 --> 00:16:44,950
What "Your Majesty"?

416
00:16:45,200 --> 00:16:47,840
Xiao Chi, you just got back.
Must you spoil the mood?

417
00:16:47,840 --> 00:16:48,200
Come.

418
00:16:48,840 --> 00:16:50,440
Let's drink a pot right now.

419
00:16:50,910 --> 00:16:53,630
Tonight, we drink until we drop.

420
00:16:57,120 --> 00:16:58,600
Yes, Your Majesty.

421
00:17:09,640 --> 00:17:10,240
It's so late.

422
00:17:10,240 --> 00:17:11,270
Why aren't you going back
to your room to rest?

423
00:17:11,270 --> 00:17:12,869
I'm waiting for the general.

424
00:17:12,920 --> 00:17:13,780
Physician Han.

425
00:17:13,920 --> 00:17:15,510
Are you going out?

426
00:17:16,680 --> 00:17:18,200
I'll go find the general for you,

427
00:17:18,200 --> 00:17:20,060
and tell him to come back earlier.

428
00:17:21,160 --> 00:17:22,020
Physician Han.

429
00:17:23,960 --> 00:17:24,619
Never mind.

430
00:17:24,720 --> 00:17:25,240
You go.

431
00:17:41,160 --> 00:17:41,960
What's wrong?

432
00:17:42,110 --> 00:17:43,710
Is something troubling you?

433
00:17:43,720 --> 00:17:44,180
It's...

434
00:17:44,510 --> 00:17:45,310
It's nothing.

435
00:17:48,000 --> 00:17:49,530
I am already in the capital.

436
00:17:49,790 --> 00:17:51,920
Why hasn’t Liu Chu come to receive me yet?

437
00:17:51,920 --> 00:17:54,070
Your Highness, you can't rush this.

438
00:17:54,480 --> 00:17:55,830
Didn’t Lord Fei say

439
00:17:55,920 --> 00:17:57,200
you’d be welcomed

440
00:17:57,350 --> 00:17:58,950
with full Jinglan ceremony?

441
00:17:59,440 --> 00:18:00,160
I hope so.

442
00:18:03,270 --> 00:18:04,730
It's like this every time.

443
00:18:04,960 --> 00:18:06,560
Xiao Chi and I are both drunk,

444
00:18:07,590 --> 00:18:09,120
but you're not drunk at all.

445
00:18:09,400 --> 00:18:10,880
Yeah, Zheng.

446
00:18:12,160 --> 00:18:13,440
That's not right.

447
00:18:14,310 --> 00:18:17,310
Your Majesty, I just look sober
on the outside.

448
00:18:18,000 --> 00:18:18,480
Look,

449
00:18:18,750 --> 00:18:19,110
I...

450
00:18:20,270 --> 00:18:21,440
can barely stand.

451
00:18:22,000 --> 00:18:22,640
Okay.

452
00:18:23,480 --> 00:18:24,440
Then sit here.

453
00:18:26,030 --> 00:18:26,960
I wouldn't dare.

454
00:18:27,160 --> 00:18:27,750
Look.

455
00:18:28,590 --> 00:18:31,750
He's still talking about etiquette
between ruler and minister.

456
00:18:31,750 --> 00:18:33,350
This means you're not drunk.

457
00:18:35,310 --> 00:18:37,920
Xiao Chi, thanks to you being here today.

458
00:18:38,160 --> 00:18:40,090
You help me teach him a harsh lesson

459
00:18:40,270 --> 00:18:41,550
and vent this anger.

460
00:18:42,550 --> 00:18:43,070
C...

461
00:18:44,350 --> 00:18:44,960
Chu,

462
00:18:45,720 --> 00:18:46,830
it's my duty.

463
00:18:47,440 --> 00:18:48,770
That was so satisfying.

464
00:18:49,720 --> 00:18:52,960
I must reward you handsomely.

465
00:18:53,640 --> 00:18:54,310
Reward me?

466
00:18:54,440 --> 00:18:55,160
Yes.

467
00:18:57,070 --> 00:18:57,930
I don't need it.

468
00:18:58,030 --> 00:18:58,680
No.

469
00:18:59,200 --> 00:19:00,860
What should I reward you with?

470
00:19:03,350 --> 00:19:03,960
The token.

471
00:19:05,270 --> 00:19:06,750
Seeing this token

472
00:19:07,070 --> 00:19:09,070
is like seeing the Emperor himself.

473
00:19:09,350 --> 00:19:11,030
In the entire capital city,

474
00:19:11,200 --> 00:19:12,920
you can go wherever you want.

475
00:19:14,830 --> 00:19:15,350
Then,

476
00:19:16,790 --> 00:19:17,960
thank you, Chu.

477
00:19:18,960 --> 00:19:20,160
I originally thought

478
00:19:21,000 --> 00:19:22,440
I would be

479
00:19:22,750 --> 00:19:25,270
a very happy and carefree prince.

480
00:19:25,920 --> 00:19:26,880
I didn't expect

481
00:19:27,440 --> 00:19:29,900
my father to suddenly
fall ill and pass away,

482
00:19:30,350 --> 00:19:31,750
passing the throne to me.

483
00:19:34,110 --> 00:19:36,040
I've never been an emperor before.

484
00:19:36,480 --> 00:19:38,080
How would I know how to be one?

485
00:19:39,000 --> 00:19:39,480
Chu,

486
00:19:40,240 --> 00:19:41,440
no matter where I am,

487
00:19:42,240 --> 00:19:43,900
no matter what you ask me to do,

488
00:19:45,750 --> 00:19:46,640
I, Xiao Chi,

489
00:19:47,110 --> 00:19:48,640
will serve you with my life.

490
00:19:48,830 --> 00:19:50,360
You always know what to say.

491
00:19:52,790 --> 00:19:54,050
Then you get him drunk.

492
00:19:56,920 --> 00:19:59,240
Get him drunk? No need.

493
00:19:59,550 --> 00:20:00,720
Drink up, Zheng.

494
00:20:00,920 --> 00:20:02,000
Okay, okay, okay.

495
00:20:02,790 --> 00:20:04,270
I accept my punishment.

496
00:20:09,830 --> 00:20:12,240
It seems we are no match for him at all.

497
00:20:12,550 --> 00:20:13,720
We can't outdrink him.

498
00:20:13,720 --> 00:20:15,270
We can only find a chance—

499
00:20:15,270 --> 00:20:17,800
when all the officials
are drinking with you,

500
00:20:18,070 --> 00:20:19,470
then we’ll get him drunk.

501
00:20:19,790 --> 00:20:20,920
A chance?

502
00:20:21,720 --> 00:20:22,830
What kind of chancer?

503
00:20:22,830 --> 00:20:25,110
Why not

504
00:20:26,480 --> 00:20:27,790
on Chi’s wedding day?

505
00:20:30,680 --> 00:20:31,400
Wedding?

506
00:20:31,720 --> 00:20:32,400
Yes.

507
00:20:33,110 --> 00:20:33,920
Well...

508
00:20:34,030 --> 00:20:36,240
Do you have a woman you like?

509
00:20:41,640 --> 00:20:42,590
No.

510
00:20:42,960 --> 00:20:43,640
No?

511
00:20:44,310 --> 00:20:45,960
All the women at the border

512
00:20:46,110 --> 00:20:47,680
want to marry General Xiao.

513
00:20:48,480 --> 00:20:49,280
Zheng, you...

514
00:20:49,590 --> 00:20:50,790
What nonsense are you talking about?

515
00:20:50,790 --> 00:20:52,240
Good for you, Xiao Chi.

516
00:20:52,790 --> 00:20:53,880
Not bad!

517
00:20:55,550 --> 00:20:56,160
Chu,

518
00:20:56,510 --> 00:20:57,880
I might be a bit

519
00:20:57,880 --> 00:20:58,590
drunk.

520
00:20:59,030 --> 00:21:00,430
I'll take my leave first.

521
00:21:03,030 --> 00:21:04,350
I'll take my leave first.

522
00:21:04,350 --> 00:21:04,720
We...

523
00:21:05,750 --> 00:21:07,590
We haven't finished the wine.

524
00:21:07,590 --> 00:21:08,240
Xiao Chi.

525
00:21:08,920 --> 00:21:10,110
General Xiao.

526
00:21:11,160 --> 00:21:11,640
This kid.

527
00:21:11,640 --> 00:21:12,440
Stop yelling.

528
00:21:12,590 --> 00:21:13,200
Do

529
00:21:13,550 --> 00:21:15,920
you have a woman you like?

530
00:21:16,920 --> 00:21:17,270
Chu.

531
00:21:17,510 --> 00:21:17,960
Yeah?

532
00:21:18,200 --> 00:21:19,330
I'll go get him back.

533
00:21:19,590 --> 00:21:20,200
Hey.

534
00:21:21,830 --> 00:21:22,830
Don't worry, Chu.

535
00:21:23,000 --> 00:21:24,730
I will definitely get him back.

536
00:21:26,110 --> 00:21:26,640
Xiao Chi.

537
00:21:27,680 --> 00:21:30,400
Then you guys can drink
with me another day.

538
00:21:32,720 --> 00:21:33,440
Buns!

539
00:21:33,440 --> 00:21:34,070
Come, drink.

540
00:21:34,070 --> 00:21:35,330
Freshly steamed buns!

541
00:21:35,400 --> 00:21:36,530
Get me another bowl.

542
00:21:38,160 --> 00:21:38,880
Buns!

543
00:21:39,240 --> 00:21:40,310
Fresh meat buns!

544
00:21:40,440 --> 00:21:41,160
Not bad.

545
00:21:41,200 --> 00:21:41,720
Miss,

546
00:21:42,000 --> 00:21:43,440
try a meat bun.

547
00:21:43,960 --> 00:21:44,720
Look.

548
00:21:47,030 --> 00:21:47,440
Ma'am,

549
00:21:47,640 --> 00:21:48,770
2 meat buns, please.

550
00:21:49,880 --> 00:21:50,400
Not bad—

551
00:21:50,920 --> 00:21:51,580
her figure.

552
00:21:52,790 --> 00:21:54,310
Do you know where the Imperial Prison is?

553
00:21:54,310 --> 00:21:55,400
The Imperial Prison?

554
00:21:55,400 --> 00:21:56,730
The Imperial Prison...

555
00:21:58,200 --> 00:21:58,800
Thank you.

556
00:22:02,200 --> 00:22:02,590
Go.

557
00:22:03,680 --> 00:22:04,640
Don't go.

558
00:22:04,920 --> 00:22:05,960
Where are you going?

559
00:22:05,960 --> 00:22:08,030
Ask me if you want to go somewhere.

560
00:22:08,440 --> 00:22:09,310
In the capital,

561
00:22:09,310 --> 00:22:11,790
there is nowhere I can't go.

562
00:22:12,200 --> 00:22:15,260
I'm going to the Imperial Prison.
Can you take me there?

563
00:22:15,550 --> 00:22:16,720
That's a good place.

564
00:22:17,070 --> 00:22:19,790
I’ve never had a woman
in the Imperial Prison before.

565
00:22:19,790 --> 00:22:20,510
Me neither.

566
00:22:20,680 --> 00:22:22,550
Just thinking about it is exciting.

567
00:22:22,550 --> 00:22:23,720
Let's go.

568
00:22:24,310 --> 00:22:24,970
You idiots!

569
00:22:25,550 --> 00:22:26,350
Let me show you

570
00:22:26,400 --> 00:22:27,800
what chili powder can do!

571
00:22:31,270 --> 00:22:31,920
After her!

572
00:22:32,070 --> 00:22:32,480
Hurry!

573
00:22:33,240 --> 00:22:33,570
Hyah!

574
00:22:34,160 --> 00:22:35,160
Stop running! Stop!

575
00:22:35,160 --> 00:22:36,160
Stop right there!

576
00:22:38,160 --> 00:22:39,030
Stop!

577
00:22:40,440 --> 00:22:41,270
I said stop!

578
00:22:41,270 --> 00:22:42,070
I'll kill you!

579
00:22:42,160 --> 00:22:42,640
Bitch!

580
00:22:42,880 --> 00:22:43,590
Stop!

581
00:22:43,830 --> 00:22:44,550
I said stop!

582
00:22:45,240 --> 00:22:45,830
After her!

583
00:22:45,830 --> 00:22:46,160
Hyah!

584
00:22:46,240 --> 00:22:46,750
After her!

585
00:22:46,750 --> 00:22:47,510
Stop!

586
00:22:49,350 --> 00:22:50,550
Still dare to fight back?

587
00:22:50,550 --> 00:22:52,000
I'll break your legs!

588
00:22:53,510 --> 00:22:54,350
Stop!

589
00:22:54,510 --> 00:22:55,110
After her!

590
00:22:56,000 --> 00:22:56,240
Hyah!

591
00:22:56,240 --> 00:22:56,880
Stop!

592
00:22:59,400 --> 00:23:00,860
Where are you going? Stop!

593
00:23:01,030 --> 00:23:01,920
I said stop!

594
00:23:03,200 --> 00:23:03,680
Run.

595
00:23:04,200 --> 00:23:05,000
Keep running.

596
00:23:05,240 --> 00:23:06,110
Why did you stop?

597
00:23:06,110 --> 00:23:07,920
There's a dead end.

598
00:23:08,680 --> 00:23:09,030
What?

599
00:23:09,790 --> 00:23:11,790
You're out of chili powder, aren't you?

600
00:23:11,790 --> 00:23:14,510
Now I can do whatever I want.

601
00:23:14,680 --> 00:23:16,160
She won't be able
to sneak attack us this time.

602
00:23:16,160 --> 00:23:17,200
Come on, get her!

603
00:23:32,790 --> 00:23:35,240
Didn't I tell you to wait
for me at the relay station?

604
00:23:35,240 --> 00:23:36,700
That's just 3 scoundrels.

605
00:23:37,440 --> 00:23:37,920
Fine.

606
00:23:38,200 --> 00:23:39,400
You’re quite capable.

607
00:23:39,400 --> 00:23:40,790
You dared to go
to the Imperial Prison alone

608
00:23:40,790 --> 00:23:42,070
to investigate your brother's case.

609
00:23:42,070 --> 00:23:43,330
You have a lot of nerve.

610
00:23:43,480 --> 00:23:45,510
Will you ride back, or go on foot?

611
00:23:46,030 --> 00:23:47,090
Riding, of course.

612
00:24:15,350 --> 00:24:17,280
Why did you come here again so late?

613
00:24:18,720 --> 00:24:19,980
You've been drinking？

614
00:24:21,030 --> 00:24:21,750
No.

615
00:24:25,880 --> 00:24:26,790
It's so late.

616
00:24:28,000 --> 00:24:29,530
Who were you drinking with?

617
00:24:29,790 --> 00:24:31,720
Xiao Chi and Fei Zheng, of course.

618
00:24:32,400 --> 00:24:33,830
Who else in this world

619
00:24:33,830 --> 00:24:35,240
is worth spending so much time

620
00:24:35,240 --> 00:24:36,700
and drinking so much with?

621
00:24:38,000 --> 00:24:39,330
I am really happy today.

622
00:24:39,680 --> 00:24:41,440
You’re this happy

623
00:24:41,720 --> 00:24:43,200
just because Xiao Chi is back?

624
00:24:43,200 --> 00:24:44,600
Not just because of that.

625
00:24:44,750 --> 00:24:46,880
It's also because he helped you expose

626
00:24:47,000 --> 00:24:49,260
Wang Ruhai's scandal in court, isn't it?

627
00:24:49,790 --> 00:24:50,550
Yes.

628
00:24:50,960 --> 00:24:53,420
You have no idea
how Wang Ruhai looked today—

629
00:24:53,750 --> 00:24:56,280
kneeling on the ground
and begging for mercy.

630
00:24:57,000 --> 00:24:59,350
I never dreamed he would have such a day.

631
00:25:00,000 --> 00:25:02,920
Xiao Chi really helped me vent my anger.

632
00:25:04,240 --> 00:25:05,960
For the first time, I felt

633
00:25:06,880 --> 00:25:09,030
what it's like to be an emperor.

634
00:25:14,160 --> 00:25:15,000
What's wrong?

635
00:25:17,030 --> 00:25:18,110
Aren't you happy?

636
00:25:19,640 --> 00:25:20,920
Did you issue the edict

637
00:25:21,640 --> 00:25:23,770
to recall Xiao Chi from Tianlang Pass?

638
00:25:27,440 --> 00:25:28,400
I think so.

639
00:25:29,030 --> 00:25:30,030
Xiao Chi

640
00:25:30,160 --> 00:25:32,160
is a key minister guarding the border,

641
00:25:32,160 --> 00:25:34,200
not a bodyguard
to escort you for the political marriage.

642
00:25:34,200 --> 00:25:35,350
Aren't you afraid

643
00:25:35,510 --> 00:25:37,590
the Changmo people
will take advantage of his absence?

644
00:25:37,590 --> 00:25:39,200
Before you did anything in the past,

645
00:25:39,200 --> 00:25:41,160
you would always discuss it with me.

646
00:25:41,160 --> 00:25:42,560
Why didn't you this time?

647
00:25:42,680 --> 00:25:43,310
Sister.

648
00:25:44,350 --> 00:25:46,550
It was a spur-of-the-moment decision.

649
00:25:47,400 --> 00:25:49,110
I swear that whatever I do in the future,

650
00:25:49,110 --> 00:25:51,240
I will definitely discuss it with you.

651
00:25:51,590 --> 00:25:52,830
Don't be mad.

652
00:25:52,830 --> 00:25:54,560
I’ll discuss it with you first,

653
00:25:54,640 --> 00:25:55,900
then issue the decree.

654
00:25:57,270 --> 00:25:58,310
You are the Emperor.

655
00:25:58,310 --> 00:25:59,310
You may decide

656
00:25:59,720 --> 00:26:01,070
as you see fit.

657
00:26:01,310 --> 00:26:02,680
You don't need to discuss with me.

658
00:26:02,680 --> 00:26:05,240
But aren't you my sister?

659
00:26:05,400 --> 00:26:06,310
I was wrong.

660
00:26:08,400 --> 00:26:11,160
I swear I'll keep my word from now on.

661
00:26:12,000 --> 00:26:13,480
Please don’t be upset.

662
00:26:16,550 --> 00:26:17,160
Please...

663
00:26:19,160 --> 00:26:20,030
I don't

664
00:26:20,030 --> 00:26:22,360
expect you to discuss everything with me.

665
00:26:22,400 --> 00:26:23,000
And I don't want to be like

666
00:26:23,000 --> 00:26:25,030
the other 3 senior ministers,

667
00:26:25,310 --> 00:26:26,710
forcing you to do things.

668
00:26:29,440 --> 00:26:30,400
In this palace, only you and I

669
00:26:30,400 --> 00:26:32,030
share the Liu bloodline

670
00:26:32,590 --> 00:26:33,880
as true kin.

671
00:26:34,750 --> 00:26:36,160
Isn't everything I do for...

672
00:26:36,160 --> 00:26:37,030
It's all for me.

673
00:26:37,030 --> 00:26:38,640
I know you did all these things

674
00:26:38,640 --> 00:26:39,480
for me.

675
00:26:39,640 --> 00:26:40,590
I understand.

676
00:26:40,590 --> 00:26:42,880
Sister, don't be mad.

677
00:26:43,640 --> 00:26:44,440
I promise

678
00:26:44,830 --> 00:26:46,430
I won't act on my own anymore.

679
00:26:46,960 --> 00:26:47,680
Okay?

680
00:26:51,550 --> 00:26:52,590
Anyway,

681
00:26:52,590 --> 00:26:53,960
I'll only say this once.

682
00:26:54,480 --> 00:26:56,340
It's up to you whether you listen.

683
00:27:00,270 --> 00:27:01,030
Lie down.

684
00:27:01,510 --> 00:27:02,200
Yes.

685
00:27:05,880 --> 00:27:06,720
Sister,

686
00:27:07,680 --> 00:27:10,920
Xiao Chi has been stationed outside
for many years.

687
00:27:11,720 --> 00:27:13,450
What should we reward him with?

688
00:27:15,550 --> 00:27:16,750
You are the emperor.

689
00:27:17,070 --> 00:27:18,470
You decide for yourself.

690
00:27:19,350 --> 00:27:20,310
But

691
00:27:20,920 --> 00:27:23,520
you have always been
in charge of the treasury.

692
00:27:23,830 --> 00:27:25,960
Why don't you decide?

693
00:27:28,270 --> 00:27:29,160
Money

694
00:27:29,880 --> 00:27:31,610
is definitely indispensable.

695
00:27:32,440 --> 00:27:34,700
We have to arrange a place
for him to live.

696
00:27:38,920 --> 00:27:40,310
I have a place in mind.

697
00:28:00,160 --> 00:28:01,880
Xiao Chi...

698
00:28:05,200 --> 00:28:07,200
General Xiao, you are finally here.

699
00:28:08,480 --> 00:28:11,960
These are the rewards
from His Majesty and the Eldest Princess.

700
00:28:11,960 --> 00:28:14,360
Thank His Majesty and the Eldest Princess.

701
00:28:15,110 --> 00:28:16,110
And there's more.

702
00:28:16,270 --> 00:28:17,160
Please take a look.

703
00:28:17,160 --> 00:28:19,160
Are you satisfied with the residence
His Majesty and the Eldest Princess

704
00:28:19,160 --> 00:28:20,160
prepared for you?

705
00:28:21,480 --> 00:28:22,510
Isn't this...

706
00:28:22,510 --> 00:28:24,920
It's the prince's mansion
before His Majesty ascended the throne.

707
00:28:24,920 --> 00:28:26,200
It's yours now.

708
00:28:26,240 --> 00:28:27,160
How can I accept this?

709
00:28:27,160 --> 00:28:29,240
It was His Majesty's
former residence.

710
00:28:29,240 --> 00:28:31,590
These are the orders
of His Majesty and the Eldest Princess.

711
00:28:31,590 --> 00:28:33,160
It's also their goodwill.

712
00:28:33,440 --> 00:28:35,500
General Xiao, please don't decline.

713
00:28:35,920 --> 00:28:36,680
In this capital,

714
00:28:36,680 --> 00:28:38,590
you must have your own residence.

715
00:28:38,590 --> 00:28:40,160
Lord Fei is right.

716
00:28:40,310 --> 00:28:42,270
I’ve carried out
the Eldest Princess’s orders.

717
00:28:42,270 --> 00:28:43,670
I shall take my leave now.

718
00:28:44,030 --> 00:28:44,630
Take care.

719
00:28:45,550 --> 00:28:46,150
Take care.

720
00:28:51,240 --> 00:28:52,480
This mansion is so big.

721
00:28:52,480 --> 00:28:55,160
We couldn't fill it
even if everyone got a room.

722
00:28:56,960 --> 00:28:58,830
Perhaps His Majesty considered this

723
00:28:58,830 --> 00:29:01,510
and let the Princess of Changmo
stay with you temporarily.

724
00:29:01,510 --> 00:29:03,000
That would be inappropriate.

725
00:29:03,000 --> 00:29:04,160
She is getting married soon.

726
00:29:04,160 --> 00:29:05,830
How can she keep living with us?

727
00:29:05,830 --> 00:29:07,110
His Majesty's will is hard to predict.

728
00:29:07,110 --> 00:29:07,960
You heard it, too.

729
00:29:07,960 --> 00:29:09,920
This is also
the Eldest Princess's order.

730
00:29:09,920 --> 00:29:10,480
As for the mansion,

731
00:29:10,480 --> 00:29:11,790
I've already had it cleaned.

732
00:29:11,790 --> 00:29:13,050
As for who lives where,

733
00:29:13,200 --> 00:29:14,860
you can decide that yourself.

734
00:29:15,240 --> 00:29:15,640
Zheng.

735
00:29:16,510 --> 00:29:18,000
Why don't you move in, too?

736
00:29:18,510 --> 00:29:19,750
Why would I move in?

737
00:29:19,830 --> 00:29:21,030
You used to live here.

738
00:29:21,270 --> 00:29:23,680
Besides, you are very familiar
with this place.

739
00:29:23,680 --> 00:29:24,510
You can stay in the South Courtyard.

740
00:29:24,510 --> 00:29:27,110
It's perfect. You can keep
an eye on them for me.

741
00:29:27,480 --> 00:29:28,310
Me keeping an eye on them?

742
00:29:28,310 --> 00:29:29,370
Then it is settled.

743
00:29:29,440 --> 00:29:31,440
I have urgent matters. I'm leaving.

744
00:29:34,160 --> 00:29:35,350
Then where does she stay?

745
00:29:35,350 --> 00:29:35,830
Who?

746
00:29:36,880 --> 00:29:37,790
Physician Han.

747
00:29:39,640 --> 00:29:40,570
East Courtyard.

748
00:29:42,640 --> 00:29:43,570
East Courtyard.

749
00:29:45,480 --> 00:29:46,830
Brat.

750
00:29:47,030 --> 00:29:49,490
Isn't that the courtyard
you used to live in?

751
00:29:52,790 --> 00:29:55,270
Everything you ordered
has been taken care of.

752
00:29:55,270 --> 00:29:56,240
After I left,

753
00:29:56,510 --> 00:29:57,550
I heard General Xiao

754
00:29:57,550 --> 00:29:59,680
also invited Lord Fei to live with him.

755
00:30:10,240 --> 00:30:11,160
This time,

756
00:30:12,000 --> 00:30:14,200
they are revisiting the old place.
